headline: Wix.com Acquires Base44 for $80 Million, Supports AI Portfolio and “Vibe Coding” Capabilities
summary: Wix.com Ltd. (NASDAQ:WIX) is one of the best technology stocks according to Wall Street analysts. On June 18, Wix.com announced its acquisition of Base44. headline: Expedia Group Stock: Is EXPE Outperforming the Consumer Cyclical Sector?
